2.6 Updated terminology: Review → Reflect
=========================================

Following David Allen's updated terminology from his more recent books,
all "review" and "oops" commands are now named "reflect":

   • ‘org-gtd-review-*’ → ‘org-gtd-reflect-*’
   • ‘org-gtd-oops-*’ → ‘org-gtd-reflect-*’

   The old names still work as aliases but are marked obsolete.


