2.11 Capture timestamps
=======================

Captured items now automatically receive an ‘ORG_GTD_CAPTURED_AT’
property with an inactive timestamp recording when the item was
captured.  This is useful for:

   • *Inbox reviews* - See how long items have been sitting in your
     inbox
   • *Weekly reviews* - Identify items that have been captured but not
     processed
   • *Auditing* - Track when ideas and tasks entered your system

   This happens automatically for all captures using the default
templates.  No configuration needed.


