          (setq org-agenda-property-position 'where-it-fits)
          (setq org-agenda-property-column 60)
          (setq org-agenda-property-separator "|")

     *NEW (org-gtd-agenda-property):*
          (setq org-gtd-agenda-property-list '("LOCATION" "DELEGATED_TO"))
          (setq org-gtd-agenda-property-position 'where-it-fits)
          (setq org-gtd-agenda-property-column 60)
          (setq org-gtd-agenda-property-separator "|")

     Steps:
       1. Remove ‘org-agenda-property’ from your package dependencies
          (no longer needed)
       2. Rename any ‘org-agenda-property-*’ variables to
          ‘org-gtd-agenda-property-*’

