4.3.4 Creating the View Function
--------------------------------

Add this to your init file (after your org-gtd configuration):

     (with-eval-after-load 'org-gtd
       (defun my-org-gtd-active-projects ()
         "Show all active projects."
         (interactive)
         (org-gtd-view-show
          '((name . "My Active Projects")
            (type . active-project)))))

   Save your init file and reload it (‘M-x eval-buffer’ or restart
Emacs).


