4.4.4 Building a Focus Work View
--------------------------------

Now let's create a view for when you have real time to focus.  You want
tasks that:
   • Are important (priority A or B)
   • Are substantial (over 30 minutes)

     (org-gtd-view-show
      '((name . "Focus Work")
        (type . next-action)
        (priority . (>= B))
        (effort . (> "30min"))))

   *What this shows:* NEXT actions that are priority B or higher AND
estimated over 30 minutes.  These are tasks worth blocking time for.


