4.4.6 Finding Tasks to Triage
-----------------------------

One more powerful pattern: finding items missing metadata.  During your
weekly review, you want to catch tasks that need estimates.

     (org-gtd-view-show
      '((name . "Needs Effort Estimate")
        (type . next-action)
        (effort . nil)))

   ‘(effort . nil)’ matches items with NO effort property set.  Same
works for priority:

     (org-gtd-view-show
      '((name . "Needs Priority")
        (type . next-action)
        (priority . nil)))

   These triage views help maintain your system.


