4.4.7 Bonus: The Clocked Filter
-------------------------------

There's one more filter: ‘clocked’.  It matches by how much time you've
*already invested* in a task.

     ;; Tasks I've started but not finished (some time clocked)
     (org-gtd-view-show
      '((name . "In Progress")
        (type . next-action)
        (clocked . (> "0:00"))))

     ;; Tasks I haven't touched yet
     (org-gtd-view-show
      '((name . "Not Started")
        (type . next-action)
        (clocked . nil)))

   *Why this is useful:* Sometimes you want to continue work you've
already invested in.  Sometimes you want fresh tasks.  The clocked
filter gives you both options.


