-----------------------------

Here's a complete setup with three views for different contexts:

     (with-eval-after-load 'org-gtd
       (defun my-quick-wins ()
         "Tasks under 15 minutes - perfect for short gaps."
         (interactive)
         (org-gtd-view-show
          '((name . "Quick Wins (< 15min)")
            (type . next-action)
            (effort . (< "15min")))))

       (defun my-focus-work ()
         "Important substantial tasks - for deep work blocks."
         (interactive)
