5.4.9 Graph Rendering Modes
---------------------------

The graph view supports two rendering modes that you can toggle between
at any time.  Configure the default mode with
‘org-gtd-graph-render-mode’.

   • SVG Mode (Default)

     High-quality graphical rendering with:
