6.5.5 Type Filters
------------------

Filter by GTD item type:

   • ‘(type . delegated)’

     *Matches*: Items with ‘ORG_GTD="Delegated"’ and TODO keyword ‘WAIT’

     *Use case*: See all delegated tasks

     *Example*:
          '((name . "All Delegations")
            (type . delegated))

   • ‘(type . calendar)’

     *Matches*: Items with ‘ORG_GTD="Calendar"’

     *Use case*: See all calendar items/appointments

     *Example*:
          '((name . "Calendar Items")
            (type . calendar))

   • ‘(type . project)’

     *Matches*: Project headings (‘ORG_GTD="Projects"’)

     *Use case*: List all projects

     *Example*:
          '((name . "All Projects")
            (type . project))

   • ‘(type . active-project)’

     *Matches*: Projects with at least one active (non-done) task

     *Use case*: See projects with work remaining

     *Example*:
          '((name . "Active Projects")
            (type . active-project))

   • ‘(type . completed-project)’

     *Matches*: Projects where all tasks are DONE

     *Use case*: Weekly review to see completed projects ready to
     archive

     *Example*:
          '((name . "Completed Projects")
            (type . completed-project))

   • ‘(type . stuck-project)’

     *Matches*: Projects with active tasks but no NEXT or WAIT tasks

     *Use case*: Find projects needing attention (dependency problems)

     *Example*:
          '((name . "Stuck Projects")
            (type . stuck-project))

   • ‘(type . tickler)’

     *Matches*: Items with ‘ORG_GTD="Tickler"’ (time-based reminders
     with review dates)

     *Use case*: Review tickler items

     *Example*:
          '((name . "Tickler Items")
            (type . tickler))

   • ‘(type . someday)’

     *Matches*: Items with ‘ORG_GTD="Someday"’ (someday/maybe with no
     specific timeframe)

     *Use case*: Review someday/maybe list

     *Example*:
          '((name . "Someday/Maybe")
            (type . someday))

   • ‘(type . habit)’

     *Matches*: Items with ‘ORG_GTD="Habits"’

     *Use case*: See all habits

     *Example*:
          '((name . "All Habits")
            (type . habit))

   • ‘(type . next-action)’

     *Matches*: Single action items (‘ORG_GTD="Actions"’) with TODO
     keyword ‘NEXT’

     *Use case*: See all single actions (not project tasks)

     *Example*:
          '((name . "Single Actions")
            (type . next-action))

   • ‘(type . tickler-project)’

     *Matches*: Projects that were moved to tickler (paused with review
     dates)

     *Use case*: Review tickler projects during weekly review

     *Note*: Consider using ‘incubated-project’ instead, which covers
     both tickler projects and someday/maybe projects.

     *Example*:
          '((name . "Tickler Projects")
            (type . tickler-project))

   • ‘(type . incubated-project)’

     *Matches*: Projects that were moved to tickler OR someday/maybe
     (paused projects)

     *Use case*: Review all incubated projects during weekly/monthly
     review.  This includes both tickler projects (with review dates)
     and someday/maybe projects (indefinitely paused).

     *Example*:
          '((name . "Incubated Projects")
            (type . incubated-project))

   • ‘(type . stuck-delegated)’

     *Matches*: Delegated items missing required metadata
     (invalid/missing timestamp OR missing "who")

     *Use case*: Find delegated items needing attention during weekly
     review

     *Example*:
          '((name . "Stuck Delegated Items")
            (type . stuck-delegated))

   • ‘(type . stuck-calendar)’

     *Matches*: Calendar items missing a valid timestamp

     *Use case*: Find calendar items that need a date set

     *Example*:
          '((name . "Stuck Calendar Items")
            (type . stuck-calendar))

   • ‘(type . stuck-tickler)’

     *Matches*: Tickler items missing a valid review date

     *Use case*: Find tickler items that need a review date

     *Example*:
          '((name . "Stuck Tickler Items")
            (type . stuck-tickler))

   • ‘(type . stuck-habit)’

     *Matches*: Habit items missing a valid scheduled date

     *Use case*: Find habits that need a schedule

     *Example*:
          '((name . "Stuck Habits")
            (type . stuck-habit))


