6.5.10 Priority, Effort, and Clocked Filters
--------------------------------------------

Filter by task metadata useful for "quick wins", "deep work", and triage
views.

   • ‘(priority . VALUE)’

     *Matches*: Items with matching priority

     *Forms*:
     ‘(priority . A)’
          Single value--matches priority A
     ‘(priority . (A B))’
          List--matches priority A OR B
     ‘(priority . (>= B))’
          Comparison--matches B or higher (A, B)
     ‘(priority . nil)’
          Items with no priority set

     *Comparison operators*: ‘<’, ‘>’, ‘<=’, ‘>=’

     *Note*: A is highest priority (A > B > C). Respects
     ‘org-priority-highest’ and ‘org-priority-lowest’ for custom ranges.

     *Example*: High priority actions:
          '((name . "High Priority")
            (type . next-action)
            (priority . A))

     *Example*: Important items (A or B):
          '((name . "Important Tasks")
            (type . next-action)
            (priority . (A B)))

     *Example*: All items B or higher:
          '((name . "Priority B+")
            (type . next-action)
            (priority . (>= B)))

     *Example*: Triage items missing priority:
          '((name . "Needs Priority")
            (type . next-action)
            (priority . nil))

   • ‘(effort . SPEC)’

     *Matches*: Items with matching Effort property

     *Forms*:
     ‘(effort . (< "0:30"))’
          Under 30 minutes
     ‘(effort . (> "1:00"))’
          Over 1 hour
     ‘(effort . (between "0:15" "1:00"))’
          Range (inclusive)
     ‘(effort . nil)’
          Items with no effort estimate

     *Duration formats* (all org-mode formats supported):
     ‘"3:12"’
          H:MM
     ‘"1:23:45"’
          H:MM:SS
     ‘"1d3h5min"’
          Units (d, h, min)
     ‘"30"’
          Bare number (minutes)

     *Example*: Quick wins (under 15 minutes):
          '((name . "Quick Wins")
            (type . next-action)
            (effort . (< "15min")))

     *Example*: Deep work items (1-2 hours):
          '((name . "Deep Work")
            (type . next-action)
            (effort . (between "1:00" "2:00")))

     *Example*: Triage items missing effort:
          '((name . "Needs Effort Estimate")
            (type . next-action)
            (effort . nil))

   • ‘(clocked . SPEC)’

     *Matches*: Items with matching total clocked time

     *Forms*:
     ‘(clocked . (< "0:30"))’
          Less than 30 minutes clocked
     ‘(clocked . (> "2:00"))’
          More than 2 hours invested
     ‘(clocked . (between "0:30" "2:00"))’
          Range (inclusive)
     ‘(clocked . nil)’
          Items with no time clocked (0 minutes)

     *Use case*: Find items you've already invested time in, or items
     you haven't started yet.

     *Example*: Items with significant time invested:
          '((name . "Deep in Progress")
            (type . next-action)
            (clocked . (> "1:00")))

     *Example*: Not started yet:
          '((name . "Not Started")
            (type . next-action)
            (clocked . nil))

     *Example*: Focus work (high priority, time invested):
          '((name . "Focus Work")
            (type . next-action)
            (priority . (>= B))
            (clocked . (> "0:30")))

   • ‘(last-clocked-out . SPEC)’

     *Matches*: Items based on when they were last clocked out

     *Forms*:
     ‘(last-clocked-out . (> "2d"))’
          Not worked on in 2+ days
     ‘(last-clocked-out . (>= "2d"))’
          Not worked on in 2+ days (inclusive)
     ‘(last-clocked-out . (< "1w"))’
          Worked on within past week
     ‘(last-clocked-out . (<= "1w"))’
          Worked on in past week (inclusive)
     ‘(last-clocked-out . nil)’
          Never clocked

     *Duration formats*:
     ‘"2d"’
          2 days
     ‘"1w"’
          1 week
     ‘"3h"’
          3 hours
     ‘"30m"’
          30 minutes

     *Project handling*: For project headings, automatically checks all
     tasks in the project and uses the most recent clock-out time.

     *Example*: Find stale projects not worked on in a week:
          '((name . "Stale Projects")
            (type . project)
            (last-clocked-out . (> "1w")))

     *Example*: Find items never started:
          '((name . "Never Started")
            (type . next-action)
            (last-clocked-out . nil))


