7.1.1 ‘org-gtd-project-map-tasks’
---------------------------------

Apply a function to each task in a project's dependency graph.

     (org-gtd-project-map-tasks FN PROJECT-MARKER)

‘FN’
     Function called with point at each task heading
‘PROJECT-MARKER’
     Marker to the project heading
Returns
     List of non-nil results from FN

   *Example*: Collect all task headlines in a project:
     (org-gtd-project-map-tasks
      (lambda () (org-get-heading t t t t))
      project-marker)

   *Example*: Sum effort estimates:
     (apply #'+ (org-gtd-project-map-tasks
                 (lambda ()
                   (or (org-duration-to-minutes
                        (org-entry-get nil "Effort")) 0))
                 project-marker))


