8.3 I can't create a project when clarifying an inbox item!
===========================================================

When organizing an item as a project, org-gtd expects a specific
structure:

     * Project heading
     ** First task
     ** Second task
     ** Third task

   *Common issues*:
   • Top-level heading must be a single asterisk ‘*’
   • Tasks must be second-level headings ‘**’
   • Must have at least one task under the project heading

   See *note data shape requirements:: for complete details.

   If this doesn't solve your problem, please open an issue at
<https://github.com/Trevoke/org-gtd.el/issues> with:
  1. The exact structure of your item in the clarify buffer
  2. What happens when you try to organize it
  3. Any error messages


